title: 269. Q&AF: Successful Comparisons, Installing Core Values & Being Silenced

description: In today's episode, Andy answers your questions on the misconception that success happens overnight, when is it an appropriate time to install core values into your company, and if he's worried about being silenced by the elite establishment.
